Socialist </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Party </ORGANIZATION> in 1966, but when the unified party took a beating in the 1968 elections the two again separated. The Social Democrats are partners with the <ORGANIZATION> Christian </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Democrats </ORGANIZATION>, Socialists, Republicans and Liberals in the governing coalition. <PERSON> Saragat </PERSON> is survived by his son and daughter. The funeral is scheduled for Monday.
