al </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Association </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Broadcasters </ORGANIZATION> on international matters. A TV signal transmitted so high in the air could cause problems for American TV stations nearby, he said.
